            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>Cumberland sausages</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>\n<p>Wipe the pan clean and return to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped sausages</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until they're browned</p>\n<p> </p>",
