      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Deseed the<strong> red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
